<div class="story"><p>Bay Ridge is a sound side subdivision in the town of Kitty Hawk with 39 building lots. There is no active home owners association and no association fee. The high ridge that Bay Ridge sits on offers a variety of sound and/or ocean views. You can find Bay Ridge just north of the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/first-flight-ridge.asp" title="First Flight Ridge">First Flight Ridge</a> and south of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/keepers-hill.asp" title="Keepers Hill">Keepers Hill</a>.</p>
